  <description type="morphology">Subshrubs, 2–4(–5) × 3–6 dm, mostly thinly tomentose. Leaves: petiole bases forming distinct ring around stem; blade elliptic, 0.2–0.6(–1) × 0.1–0.3(–0.4) cm. Inflorescences virgate or cymose; branches usually slender. Involucres 2–3 mm. Flowers 3–4 mm; perianth white to pink or rose. Achenes 2.5–3 mm.</description>
